# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok seven chinese cities , namely , tianjin , shijiazhuang , taiyuan , hohhot , changsha , chongqing and lanzhou , reported slight air pollution today , with the highest pollution reading at ### in taiyuan .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (c / city
            :quant 7
            :location (c2 / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "China"))
            :ARG1-of (m / mean-01
                  :ARG2 (a / and
                        :op1 (c3 / city
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Tianjin"))
                        :op2 (c4 / city
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Shijiazhuang"))
                        :op3 (c5 / city
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Taiyuan"))
                        :op4 (c6 / city
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Hohhot"))
                        :op5 (c7 / city
                              :name (n6 / name
                                    :op1 "Chongqing"))
                        :op6 (c8 / city
                              :name (n7 / name
                                    :op1 "Lanzhou")))))
      :ARG1 (p / pollute-01
            :ARG0 (a2 / air)
            :degree (s / slight))
      :time (t / today)
      :ARG0-of (c9 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (r2 / read-01
                  :ARG3 (p2 / pollute-01)
                  :location c
                  :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                        :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
                              :ARG1 r2)
                        :ARG3 (m2 / most)))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok some ### more british soldiers from their cyprus bases are expected to fly to iraq thursday evening and another ### will go this weekend , english-language daily cyprus mail reported .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (m / mail
            :mod (l / language
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "English"))
            :frequency (r2 / rate-entity-91
                  :ARG3 (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (d / day)))
            :topic (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Cyprus")))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (e / expect-01
                  :ARG1 (f / fly-01
                        :ARG1 (s / soldier
                              :mod (c2 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Great"
                                          :op2 "Britain"))
                              :quant (s2 / some))
                        :destination (c3 / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Iraq"))
                        :time (d2 / date-entity
                              :weekday (t2 / thursday)
                              :dayperiod (e2 / evening))))
            :op2 (g / go-02
                  :ARG0 (a2 / another)
                  :time (w / weekend
                        :mod (t3 / this)))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok us shares opened higher as bargain-hunters swooped in after a five-week slump for the major indexes .
# ::alignments
(o / open-01
      :ARG1 (s / share
            :poss (w / we))
      :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
            :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
                  :ARG1 o)
            :ARG3 (m / more))
      :time (s2 / swoop-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h3 / hunt-01
                        :ARG1 (b / bargain-01)))
            :time (a / after
                  :op1 (s3 / slump-01
                        :ARG1 (ii / index
                              :ARG1-of (m2 / major-02))
                        :duration (t / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 5
                              :unit (w2 / week))))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the international hockey federation announced sunday it found insufficient evidence to prove claims of match-rigging between india and malaysia during the pre-olympic tournament in barcelona early this year .

                        :ARG1 (l / link-01

                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "India"))
                              :ARG2 (c2 / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Malaysia"))
                              :time (t2 / tournament
                                    :time (b / before
                                          :op1 (e2 / event
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "olympic"
                                                      :op2 "Games")))
                                    :location (c3 / city
                                          :name (n4 / name
                                                :op1 "Barcelona"))
                                    :time (e3 / early
                                          :op1 (y / year
                                                :mod (t3 / this)))))
                        :ARG0-of (s / suffice-01
                              :polarity -)))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / sunday))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok seven afghan soldiers were killed saturday evening in an ambush by suspected taliban militants in the southern province of helmand , a senior police official said on sunday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / police
                        :mod (s2 / senior))
                  :ARG2 (o / official)))
      :ARG1 (k / kill-01
            :ARG0 (a / ambush-01
                  :ARG0 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of h
                        :ARG1 (c / criminal-organization
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Taliban"))
                        :ARG2 (m / militant)
                        :ARG2-of (s3 / suspect-01)))
            :ARG1 (s4 / soldier
                  :quant 7
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Afghanistan")))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s5 / saturday)
                  :dayperiod (e / evening)))
      :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
            :ARG0 a)
      :location (p4 / province
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 " helmand")
            :location (s6 / south)))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok danny koevermans was included friday in the netherlands squad to face romania and slovenia in #### european championship qualifiers , one day after the az alkmaar striker scored a goal and created a second against newcastle in the uefa cup .
# ::alignments
(ii / include-91
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Danny"
                  :op2 "Koevermans"))
      :ARG2 (s / squad
            :poss (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Netherlands")))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :purpose (f2 / face-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (t / team
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Romania"))
                  :op2 (t2 / team
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Slovenia")))
            :subevent-of (q / qualify-02
                  :ARG2 (g / game
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "European"
                              :op2 "Championship"
                              :op3 "Championship"))))
      :time (a2 / after
            :op1 (a3 / and
                  :op1 (s2 / score-01
                        :ARG0 (p2 / person
                              :ARG0-of (s3 / strike-02)
                              :mod (t3 / team
                                    :name (n6 / name
                                          :op1 "Az"
                                          :op2 "Albania")))
                        :ARG1 (g2 / goal))
                  :op2 (c2 / create-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (g3 / goal
                              :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                                    :value 2))
                        :ARG4 (t4 / team
                              :name (n7 / name
                                    :op1 "Newcastle"))
                        :subevent-of (c3 / cup
                              :mod (o2 / organization
                                    :name (n8 / name
                                          :op1 "Uefa")))))
            :quant (t5 / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (d2 / day))))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the asian development bank -lrb- adb -rrb- will provide loans worth #.### billion u.s. dollars and non - refundable aid worth ## million u.s. dollars for a technical assistance program to vietnam for the ####-#### period , vietnam news agency -lrb- vna -rrb- reported saturday .

      :ARG0 (a / agency

            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Vietnam")))
      :ARG1 (p / provide-01
            :ARG0 (b / bank
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Leb-vna-rrb")
                  :mod (d / develop-02)
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Asia")))
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (l / loan-01
                        :ARG1-of (w / worth-01
                              :ARG2 (m / monetary-quantity
                                    :quant 1000000000
                                    :unit (d2 / dollar
                                          :mod (c3 / country
                                                :name (n5 / name
                                                      :op1 "U.S."))))))
                  :op2 (a3 / aid-01
                        :ARG1-of (r2 / refund-01
                              :ARG1-of (p2 / possible-01
                                    :polarity -))
                        :ARG1-of (w2 / worth-01
                              :ARG2 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                                    :quant 1000000
                                    :unit (d3 / dollar
                                          :mod c3)))))
            :ARG2 c
            :purpose (p3 / program
                  :ARG0-of (a4 / assist-01
                        :ARG2 (t / technical))
                  :purpose (p4 / period
                        :time-of (t2 / thing
                              :ARG1-of r
                              :ARG0 a))))
      :time (d4 / date-entity
            :weekday (s / saturday)))

                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "U.S."))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (p3 / person
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Israel")))
            :op2 (p4 / person
                  :mod (c3 / country
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Palestine"))))
      :ARG2 (a2 / and
            :op1 (f / find-01
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (w / way
                        :manner-of (r / resume-01
                              :ARG0 a
                              :ARG1 (n5 / negotiate-01
                                    :ARG0 a))))
            :op2 (a3 / avoid-01
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (a4 / act-02
                        :mod (u2 / unilateral)
                        :ARG0-of (p5 / prevent-01
                              :ARG1 (a5 / agree-01)
                              :ARG1-of (p6 / possible-01)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::alignments
(h / head-02
      :ARG0 (s / stock
            :mod (c / company
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "U.S.")))
      :ARG1 (o / open-02
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (m / monday))
            :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (h3 / high-02
                        :ARG1 o)
                  :ARG3 (m2 / more
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / sharp-02))))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (o2 / outline-01
                  :ARG0 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (g / government-organization
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Federal"
                                    :op2 "Reserve"))
                        :op2 (g2 / government-organization
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Tenth"
                                    :op2 "Department")))
                  :ARG1 (s3 / step-01
                        :ARG1-of (a3 / aim-02
                              :ARG2 (s4 / shore-up-01
                                    :ARG1 (c2 / confident-01
                                          :ARG1 (a4 / and
                                                :op1 (c3 / company
                                                      :name (n4 / name
                                                            :op1 "Fannie"
                                                            :op2 "Mae"))
                                                :op2 (c4 / company
                                                      :name (n5 / name
                                                            :op1 "Freddie"
                                                            :op2 "Mac"))
                                                :mod (m3 / mortgage)))))))))
